race.comment: BULL DURHAM (1) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 4 lengths away in second (22.66) at Geelong in a Grade 5 over 400m. Key chance in this line up. PAW RIVAL (8) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (22.98) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can find the frame this time. SAKURA RYKER (2) found trouble in the run here last time and failed to finish. Key chance on best form. DARNUM BEAR (5) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.
